---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dumpster Machine | America's Straight-Shooting Dumpster Rental">
	<main>
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="bg-slate-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-36">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-100">
				<!-- Full Width Dumpster Background -->
				<div class="w-full h-full bg-[url('/hero-bg.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/80 via-slate-900/40 to-transparent"></div>
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tighter uppercase text-white">
					No Hidden Fees. <br class="hidden md:block"/>
					<span class="text-green-600">No Surprises.</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-slate-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
					Tackling a big project? Let us handle the waste. Kick back and relax—<strong class="text-white bg-green-600/30 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-green-500/50">you don't even need to be home for delivery!</strong> We run the logistics so you don't have to.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
					<a href="#quote" class="bg-green-600 text-slate-900 font-black text-xl px-10 py-5 rounded-sm shadow-[6px_6px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:translate-y-[4px] hover:translate-x-[4px] transition-all uppercase tracking-wider block sm:inline-block">
						Find My City & Price
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Guarantees Section -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase text-slate-900 tracking-tight">The Dumpster Machine Difference</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mt-4 font-medium max-w-3xl mx-auto">We aren't just another waste company playing games with your schedule and your wallet. We offer rock-solid guarantees, transparent pricing, and a stress-free rental experience from drop-off to pickup.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<!-- Guarantee 1 -->
					<div class="bg-white p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-900 text-green-600 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black mb-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">1</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900">The $50 On-Time Guarantee</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							If we don't deliver on the day we agreed to, we refund you $50. Period. And we will never leave you hanging for two business days. We put our money where our mouth is.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Guarantee 2 -->
					<div class="bg-white p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-900 text-green-600 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black mb-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">2</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900">Transparent, Flat-Rate Pricing</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							Every dumpster comes with a generous weight allowance included in the price. We put that number in bold print—not buried in a contract. No hidden 'processing' fees, and no bait-and-switch. You know exactly what you'll pay.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Guarantee 3 -->
					<div class="bg-white p-10 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(22,163,74,1)] border-4 border-slate-900 rounded-sm">
						<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-900 text-green-600 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-black mb-6 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)]">3</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-4 text-slate-900">You Don't Need To Be Home</h3>
						<p class="text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
							Schedule your delivery for the day before your project starts, and we'll give you that extra day for FREE. That way, the dumpster is already sitting exactly where you need it when you're ready to start. Zero waiting around.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- The Pitch Section -->
		<section class="py-24 bg-green-600 border-y-8 border-slate-900">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="bg-slate-900 p-12 shadow-[12px_12px_0px_rgba(255,255,255,1)] border-4 border-white rounded-sm text-white">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase mb-6 text-green-600">Fair Pricing. Exceptional Service.</h2>
					<p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium text-slate-200">
						We partner exclusively with top-tier, fully-insured local crews who treat your property with respect.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
						We do things by the book to ensure your driveway and property stay protected. We handle all the logistics and coordination behind the scenes, so your dumpster arrives exactly when you need it with absolutely no hassle.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
